## 7. Operational Forecast (scripts/run_forecast.py)

This is the operational forecast stage. Predictions are made for specific future years outside the test period.

### 7.1 Execution Flow

```
scripts/run_forecast.py
  └─▶ forecast.py  (load weights → construct support → inner adapt → predict)
  └─▶ src/forecast_draw.py  (visualize results)
```

### 7.2 Configuration

- **Weight path:** Set the model weight file path in `forecast.py` to the trained checkpoint
- **Support construction:** Stratified sampling of 5 years from the 20-year window preceding target year t (t−20 to t−1)
- **Prediction output:** Per-member predictions, ensemble mean, ensemble spread (uncertainty estimate)

```bash
cd scripts/
python run_forecast.py

cd ../src/
python forecast_draw.py
```

> ⚠️ Before running `run_forecast.py`, verify that the weight file path (checkpoint path) and input data path in the script are correctly configured for the current server environment.

